SENATE SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4420
A bill to amend 1984 PA 431, entitled
"The management and budget act,"
(MCL 18.1101 to 18.1594) by adding section 364a.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 364a. (1) The public disclosure form for a legislatively
2 directed spending item required under section 364 must be submitted
3 in the following form:
4 Legislatively Directed Spending Item Information
5 1. Sponsoring legislator's full name:
6 2. Cosponsoring legislators' names (if applicable):
7 3. Intended legislatively directed spending item recipient:
