19 Signature: ____________________________________
20 (2) As used in this section:
21 (a) "Immediate family member" means any of the following
22 individuals:
23 (i) An individual's parent, child, sibling, or spouse.
24 (ii) Any other individual who resides in the same household as
25 the individual.
26 (b) "Legislatively directed spending item" means that term as
27 defined in section 364.
28 (c) "Legislator" means a duly elected individual who serves in
29 either the senate or house of representatives.
