1 (d) "Staff member" means an individual who is currently or,
2 within the prior 2 years, has been employed by the senate or house
3 of representatives.
4 Enacting section 1. This amendatory act does not take effect
5 unless Senate Bill No. 596 of the 103rd Legislature is enacted into
6 law.
